Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur4}我在等著
